snippet.title: "Bureau of Contacts" horror game: teaser
snippet.description:
Bureau of Contacts - first PC horror game where a neural network is trained to kill. 

Planned for Early Access during Summer 2024.

Wishlist & Follow on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2840210/Bureau_of_Contacts/
